name: i3 Group
tag_list: payroll-processing, individual-taxation, income-tax, social-security-laws, payroll, payroll-outsourcing
overview: i3Group is an Australia-based firm that specializes in payroll outsourcing services. The company has a highly experienced staff on its team working for clients across many sectors of the industry. The firm understands the difficulties in handling payroll and hence works to simplify the process at a reasonable cost. The services offered are customized to fit the requirements of the clients. The company has a remarkable human resource information system that allows its clients to access and manage their employee data. Today, i3Group boasts of its success with a hundred percent client retention rate and is one of the leading payroll outsourcing firms in Australia.
